    <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will be implemented on Vyksas and Gubakhas production sites. The first one is located in Vyksa town in Nizhegorodskaya Oblast (186 km from Nizhniy Novgorod, the regional capital). The plant is conveniently located close by railway, automobile and waterway transportation routes. Gubakha is located in Perm Region, in western slopes of the Middle Urals, within the Kosva river valley and in-between mountains near the Chusovoy-Solikamsk railway.</narrative>
